{"tid":2117560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得兩條路，請選擇，一係零感染，一係暴到七彩。","createTime":"2020-07-21T02:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T02:43:39.000Z","uid":212702,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c46dd19b1ffcb81e2cdc9e121712992d6e4fa7","tid":2117560,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭政府係抗疫上睇得出有好重政治考慮，希望保持零星過案，死一兩件無問題，方便政治操作。<br />\n當然，病毒唔係柒婆話點就點，如今香港人只有兩條路。<br />\n1，大家請認真攜手抗疫，做到零個案，保住香港。<br />\n2，爆佢老母西，爆到七彩，死6/7成老嘢，就咁睇死藍廢老佔比例多好多，到時柒婆仲大鑊。<br />\n<br />\n正評：零個案<br />\n負評：暴佢老母西"},{"pid":"3d966423b42721b13a50a8ace16dd7152d4d0325","tid":2117560,"uid":56550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"爆佢老母西！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f99906d2bf6e2296557acd06aab1c7d8d8568f","tid":2117560,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"爆啦好悶呀"},{"pid":"65be8b723e638f51b2d9a45d44499554249cd629","tid":2117560,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"武肺大爆發先係對社會最有利<br />\n<br />\n又可以解決人口老化<br />\n<br />\n又可以增加年輕人向上流動機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況後生中武肺同中次感冒無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c85f196d7bca80e439d16d98b491f7db497e0d","tid":2117560,"uid":8313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"爆佢老母西，死多啲廢老，種票都冇得種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652efc5393992cdcbcb2599e0fe5fb3dbebca080","tid":2117560,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"唔係大多數人已經選擇攬炒咩<img src=\"/ass